<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>PL Lab 지원 완료</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --naver-green: #03c75a;
            --naver-green-dark: #009f47;
            --naver-gray: #8e8e8e;
            --naver-light-gray: #f5f6f7;
            --naver-border: #e6e6e6;
            --naver-text: #333333;
            --naver-error: #ff3a35;
            --naver-background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', sans-serif;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .button {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--naver-background);
            color: var(--naver-text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 15px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: pageLoad 0.3s ease-out forwards;
        }

        @keyframes pageLoad {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .success-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .success-header {
            background-color: var(--naver-green);
            color: white;
            padding: 35px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .success-header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .success-header p {
            font-size: 17px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .success-icon-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: -50px auto 25px;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .success-icon-circle {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--naver-green);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transform: scale(0);
            animation: circleAppear 0.35s ease forwards 0.2s;
        }

        .success-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            color: white;
            transform: scale(0);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: checkAppear 0.35s ease forwards 0.55s;
        }

        @keyframes circleAppear {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0);
            }
            60% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        @keyframes checkAppear {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0) rotate(-45deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            70% {
                transform: scale(1.2) rotate(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(1) rotate(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .success-content {
            padding: 0 40px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .success-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--naver-text);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .success-message {
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .info-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .info-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--naver-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .info-title svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .info-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .info-item {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #4b5563;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .info-item-dot {
            color: var(--naver-green);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--naver-green);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(3, 199, 90, 0.2);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--naver-green-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(3, 199, 90, 0.3);
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .success-header h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .success-header p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .success-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .success-content {
                padding: 0 20px 30px;
            }

            .info-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="success-header">
            <h1>PL Lab</h1>
            <p>2025학년도 연구원 모집 지원서</p>
        </div>

        <div class="success-icon-wrapper">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <div class="success-icon-circle">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="success-content">
            <h2 class="success-title">지원이 성공적으로 완료되었습니다</h2>
            <p class="success-message">
                PL Lab에 관심을 가져주셔서 감사합니다.<br>
                귀하의 지원서가 정상적으로 접수되었습니다.
            </p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    다음 절차 안내
                </div>
                <div class="info-list">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span class="info-item-dot">•</span>
                        <span>서류 심사 결과는 지원서에 기재한 이메일로 개별 안내됩니다.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span class="info-item-dot">•</span>
                        <span>서류 심사 합격자에 한해 면접 일정이 안내될 예정입니다.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span class="info-item-dot">•</span>
                        <span>지원 관련 문의사항은 pllab1004@gmail.com 으로 연락 주시기 바랍니다.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>